{
  "logNo": "220881252185",
  "title": "추운겨울에 하는 따뜻한 회식 in 경복궁 [남성역 경희 이수한의원]",
  "addDate": "2016. 12. 8.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220881252185",
  "html_size": 201165,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220881252185\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220881252185\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>오래간만이죠?</p><p><br /></p><p>ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p>오래간만에 이수한의원 식구들도 회식을했습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>저번달 11월에 저희가 듣고온 강의가 있었는데</p><p>아쉽게도 원장님은 못가시고 저희 직원들만 다녀왔어요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그래서 직원들이 각자 들은 강의 내용&nbsp;파트를 원장님께 발표했습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>발표는 처음이라 좀&nbsp;부족했지만 그래도 성공적이었습니다 ㅎㅎ</p><p>(나만 이렇게 생각하나? ^^ 잘햇다고 원장님이 박수도 쳐주시고 칭찬도 해주셨는데.. ㅎㅎ</p><p>그래서 성공적이라고 굳게 믿고싶은 1인 ㅎㅎ)</p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e67e8e0f058d9a3f.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-86\"></a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>발표가 끝나고 원장님께서 식당에 예약 해놓으셨다 하셔서 다 같이 저녁식사를 하러 갔습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>남성역 이수한의원에서 조금 떨어진 사당역에</p><p>파스텔시티 안에 있는 \"경복궁\"이라는 레스토랑입니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>레스토랑에 입장하는 순간부터 직원들의 태도나 말투에 먼저 집중합니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>아무래도 발표를 하고 가서 그런지 더 집중하게 되네요 ㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8b4ff4f48c93751d.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMjcw/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAxMzIy.VRlP-M0QI7pVJ4-Hdou4qM3Tv8xzcv-hXpxgyTQKgR4g.NOgWZ6Syh9ekw-S9SucU-GznKV589MWBhgIpFDIeq6cg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111138061.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8b4ff4f48c93751d.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>조명이 참 이쁘죠</p><p><br /></p><p>램프만 찍으려고 했는데</p><p>\"경복궁\" 이라고 써있어서</p><p><br /></p><p>좀 더 집중해서 찍었는데</p><p>ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p>그냥 찍은거랑 다른게 없을거 같네요&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>경복궁은 고객님의 건강을 최우선으로 생각한다 합니다</p><p>소금 하나에도 명품만을 고집할정도로..</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMDhfMjQx/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAxNjAw.W_5EqXwe1VWEWIeb9ynR0WTRtCBq9rik4Wv4etBuvpEg.rSkezudPaRKwmKEkVlqefORJFQxHtM6MLFfL_caOlJwg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111138621.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMjQx/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAxNjAw.W_5EqXwe1VWEWIeb9ynR0WTRtCBq9rik4Wv4etBuvpEg.rSkezudPaRKwmKEkVlqefORJFQxHtM6MLFfL_caOlJwg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111138621.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNjEyMDhfMjQx/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAxNjAw.W_5EqXwe1VWEWIeb9ynR0WTRtCBq9rik4Wv4etBuvpEg.rSkezudPaRKwmKEkVlqefORJFQxHtM6MLFfL_caOlJwg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111138621.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>따뜻한 물과함께</p><p>주문한 음식을 기다리면서...<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8fce5e1498346d64.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfODYg/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAxODA4.sSWLwWgAqVBycExsjFineNOLgnOLCvxPHi3ylsI1YO4g.MIfPqLoi06s-n9ZlfMnwLunTs5TOODWyGZ7C-qxfk7sg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111139083.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8fce5e1498346d64.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>수저 &amp; 젓가락도 골드에요</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>임금님인줄&nbsp;</p><p>ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>오늘음식은 코스요리로 주문을 했습니다</p><p><br /></p><p>제일 처음 나온 음식은</p><p><br /></p><p>동치미랑 죽이나왔는데 사진이 어디로갔지 ㅠㅠ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그럼 그 다음 음식부터 시작하겠습니다</p><p><br /></p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6918cee02fb5d19f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTAz/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAyMDU5.Y_x2GjdRs_0sRegAvV-FfPEL42A2oD70YPCG2cZ3kSUg.iVZDsV-f4_mxhqI2gU37-Wup16Vm3yGgdY5Qlly6Kwwg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111139525.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6918cee02fb5d19f.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>쌈페이퍼안에 고기와 야채가 들어있는데 무쌈으로 감싼은식인데..</p><p>이게 무쌈때문에 상큼하고 쌈페이퍼 때문에 쫄깃하고 맛있었어요</p><p><br /></p><p>플레이팅도 심플하고 이쁘죠<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7af8c1e4fe10ea2c.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTAz/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAyMjUz.q75lm04nkWJQJRCCC7wo3ioFPihEu5unMW2291lsiJ4g.SF0pV2OVx0sSGZeieYDi9YTRtTfniNoflgWINX8GS0wg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111140023.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/7af8c1e4fe10ea2c.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>회도 나오고</p><p>제일 먼저 손에 간 이쁜주황색 연어회 ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p>간장이 찍어먹으니 꿀맛</p><p><br /></p><p>가운데 꽃도 이쁘죠잉? 생화에요&nbsp;</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d1b7465cc22217a.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTg3/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAyNDgx._toY-hv83QT3zc8A1p7h8SfpJOw3MrPmXmebb0zSBAgg.1A3cCm9-gJyGmoQ1EbZsu-hSVyU6FsTeHfgsOO2NDaYg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111140492.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2d1b7465cc22217a.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>샐러드가 처음에 나올땐 이쁘게 장식해서 나왔는데</p><p>사진찍어야는데 직원분이 먹기 좋게 잘라주시는 바람에 모양은 다 망가짐 ㅠㅠ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>이거 엄청 새콤하고 맛있어요</p><p>완전 내 스타일</p><p><br /></p><p>양상추도 토마토도 새우도 다 맛있다</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/28546cfd2d2e59f7.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMjMz/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAyNjgy.-vAACHlQz-H2ZPTaCrIsa_YMLaRwkE80GylFNj--60og.N6oTBNM-jZSo4-FfKPwtG8q4yOUOxyek3Od8v52jFr0g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111140971.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/28546cfd2d2e59f7.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>이거는.. 그닥 손이 별로 안갔던 음식인데&nbsp;</p><p>면이.. 밀가루가 아니여서 그랬나 ㅋㅋ</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a75afe113165cbf2.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTc3/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAyODk4.TqYCqg6ABUN0bHp2MB9L6fPNdHFLLsEGg0RxUKkAdpQg.AQO2kRltwCqeJbjFd7TO00OsFIHjeVq3t9pKCTyeZYUg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111141514.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a75afe113165cbf2.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그 다음</p><p>고기가 나온다고 반찬을 주시고&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/20c12448c23cfb40.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTI1/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAzMTE5.cc7dao91KbTQgZiR72GwY-pxyoc0y0vK4h06SHFJGxUg.UK7T0zaltniz7cHm9FkhsOfZXYFwp5ngD_EbbJQ61CMg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111142014.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/20c12448c23cfb40.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1d947c03619a4dfd.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfODQg/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAzMzIw.WY0ki2OYL2npmTXkKnHiDIzHHBQ9qzMOaNIzZ61KJNIg.ba-m8tyEufjwuM9Wa7vgIVNWX9enXvVX5B2dJRJ37fAg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111142664.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1d947c03619a4dfd.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/318aec6c33b4b044.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMjk1/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAzNTQ4.Z2aPq3nNv20weQ1oDkEsEX75aIdYh-xoFYj7CbctEgMg.FUhyrKyFx3W-G8FfQV6BVrMhokSwfs97wEFmBckWfk0g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111143040.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/318aec6c33b4b044.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>드디어 메인인 갈비를....</p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4eb419c0c9986d29.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-88\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>두둥</p><p><br /></p><p>지금 사진으로만 봐도 입에 침이 고이네.. 추룹~</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ee888371165a5f6a.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfNjkg/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAzNzQ3.boo45I4m2pXtvMzCFwqlqaFc720rICWF6QyNfHO-iMkg.54gfJpFt9OPs3AfO001GduRWw4UKrfIZhlUgWx0Tqjcg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111143436.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ee888371165a5f6a.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>직원분계서 직접 구워주시고 계셔서</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그동안 우리는 재밌는 대화를 했습니다 ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그리고 먹기 좋게 한입크기로 잘라주셔서 바로 먹을수 있었지요</p><p><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/da532e674bdb70d3.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTk5/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTAzOTIz.jbpBYAZqRyzKgh_m5cswiqCBac4wUx76EDVoMwZ7jgYg.JIajc6DsgEO6bgK2DDycty_bU-inrxeKA5OdDGFDVagg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111143911.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/da532e674bdb70d3.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>짠!</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그리고 중간에 생선..탕수육? 도 나오고..</p><p>이것도 엄청 맛있었다</p><p><br /></p><p>생선 살이 너무 부드러움<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/18339dceaca45747.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMTU4/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTA0MTQy.qRxnMijBWETsliF3SCkk8vKmx6LjYC3RLrw4JMZ-s8Eg.kJ8gGV1auB1VK_4fxNonOjOFbWvlemHxzowbSnSdoigg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111144354.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/18339dceaca45747.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b9e5175717f03720.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfNzQg/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTA0NTAz.BavUAZkzbAlvBbCvYf4oA2su6pG2qp4DEAtIl0jnEJMg.7MifXgFNJp4iMQsy74rfkRDPJNzfBC1TiZ7LGF0UKKog.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111144855.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b9e5175717f03720.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>해물탕인가... 오징어 조개도 있고 두부가 너무 푸딩같아서 입에서 녹는다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>이제 코스요리 중 마지막이라고 밥을 주신다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>반찬 세가지랑<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c9b9a39dee9d063b.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfMjQy/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTA0Njk4.mx03x2ZKbDg8hCHIkJ2w8Y174UPdeMWdpXP9KxquwWog.0Z58sTMP06h7z-UGdfjfnTatv2cJq0t7HHbJPuhD6wQg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111145292.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c9b9a39dee9d063b.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92f51a72e4a3180f.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 480px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"MjAxNjEyMDhfNzgg/MDAxNDgxMTY3NTA0OTEx.dXn9J2b9g7nA_vXzT5oB725TWuVGC_l0406waEPz5rMg.wx6_8vERS0ywfbu8K9IhPVVkOZmvu7H0618pupQk0X4g.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20161208_111145841.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336D8C6F59')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92f51a72e4a3180f.jpg\">&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p>밥 &amp; 된장찌개</p><p><br /></p><p>밥이랑 찌개랑 반찬이 너무 간단하게 나와서 오히려 다행이다 ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>휴</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>너무 많이 먹었다</p><p><br /></p><p>(나는 항상 많이 먹지만.. 오늘도 많이 먹었다..</p><p>...는 안비밀이다 하지만 비밀인척한다 ㅎㅎㅎㅎ)</p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/56fef83e8c42359e.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-4\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>배가 터질거같았다</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>너무너무 잘먹었습니다 ^^</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>강의발표한거 잊지않게 계속 숙지해서&nbsp;</p><p>우리 이수한의원이 잘 되게 열심히 해야지</p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/6118dbf5bc5723bc.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-23\"></a>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>근대 이거 블로그 올릴때마다 드는 생각인데&nbsp;</p><p>회식하면 그 레스토랑 홍보하는거 같다 ㅠㅠ #힝&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
